THE SPECS

TEach Cartel NFT is unique and programmatically generated from over 170 possible traits, including expression, headwear, clothing, and more. All Cartels are amazing, but some are rarer than others.

The NFTs are stored as ERC-721 tokens on the Ethereum blockchain and hosted on IPFS Purchasing an NFT varies in price.

To access members-only areas such as THE TRAPHOUSE, NFT holders will need to be signed into their Metamask Wallet.
